review_text: A very nice park, no bathroom though
Nice place, quite and good for kids

(Translated by Google) Very nice park

(Original)
Très beau parc

(Translated by Google) This park is not very big. It is not as busy as some parks in this borough. I like to go there because very often my son finds himself alone. Which is not so bad in this time of pandemic.

(Original)
Ce parc n'est pas très grand. Il n'est pas aussi achalandé que certains parcs dans cet arrondissement. J'aime bien y aller car très souvent, mon fils se retrouve seul. Ce qui n'est pas si mal en ce temps de pandémie.

(Translated by Google) It is especially the person who accompanied me❤

(Original)
C'est surtout la personne qui m'accompagnait❤

(Translated by Google) Very nice little park

(Original)
Tres beau petit parc
